title: Xi Jinping's 2020 Announcement. #Satire
description:
Chinese propaganda is so close to self-parody, that it's nearly impossible to offer any kind of satirical commentary.  This video was made with some vocal/editorial assistance from Simon Rex; you can find his youtube channel here: https://www.youtube.com/user/dirttothenasty/videos?view=0&sort=dd&shelf_id=0
#XiJinping #SimonRex #DirtNasty
